<use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vqc1665703032032.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vqc1665703032032.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vqc1665703032032.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vqc1665703032032\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Snippet\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__snippet_315543\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Snippet is a Development Object that defines a fragment of code or text that can be inserted into code.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__p_d96098e1_d96099e1_d96100e1\">A Snippet can be any text string, ranging from a single word, to a complete script module. For example, it can be an HTML element or collection of elements, a ProcScript fragment, a style definition, a JavaScript construction, or any other kind of text. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"biv1704450635249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biv1704450635249.html\" title=\"Snippets are named fragments of code or text that you can insert into your application script or layout to speed development. They are defined as development objects in snippet libraries.\">Snippets</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__topic_d64192e1_d64193e1_d64194e1_d64195e1_d64196e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d430431e63\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__image_dzt_hts_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/code_snippet.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">snp</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vhx1665702714312.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhx1665702714312.html\" title=\"A Snippet Library contains code Snippets that can copied and pasted into your code during development.\">Snippet Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10661e1_d10662e1_d10663e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">libsnp:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>/snp:<var class=\"keyword varname\">Snippet.Syntax</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__topic_d64197e1_d64198e1_d64199e1_d64200e1_d64201e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d430431e269\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__p_d96107e1_d96108e1_d96109e1\">Snippet specializes Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__li_d38906e1_d38907e1_d38908e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__p_d96110e1_d96111e1_d96112e1\">It has an Snippet Library as parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__li_d38909e1_d38910e1_d38911e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__p_d96113e1_d96114e1_d96115e1\">It is used as a resource during development. It has no runtime equivalent.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__topic_d64202e1_d64203e1_d64204e1_d64205e1_d64206e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d430431e293\">\n                     \n Properties\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Snippet Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property Name</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Name</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Name of the snippet.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Syntax</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Coding language; one of: <code class=\"ph codeph\">procscript</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">html</code>, or <var class=\"keyword varname\">UserDefined</var> (such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">js</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">css</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">txt</code>).</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Category</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">User-defined category that can be used to group snippets.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Text</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Code fragment.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Description</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Brief description of the snippet.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Documentation</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vqc1665703032032__table_d10664e1_d10665e1_d10666e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Longer description of the snippet and its uses.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616573\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616573\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Snippet Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Snippet A Snippet is a Development Object that defines a fragment of code or text that can be inserted into code. A Snippet can be any text string, ranging from a single word, to a complete script module. For example, it can be an HTML element or collection of elements, a ProcScript fragment, a style definition, a JavaScript construction, or any other kind of text. For more information, see Snippets . Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: snp Main Development Object? No Part of: Snippet Library Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: libsnp: LibraryName /snp: Snippet.Syntax Specialization Snippet specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has an Snippet Library as parent. It is used as a resource during development. It has no runtime equivalent. Properties Table 1. Snippet Properties Property Name Description Name Name of the snippet. Syntax Coding language; one of: procscript , html , or UserDefined (such as js , css , or txt ). Category User-defined category that can be used to group snippets. Text Code fragment. Description Brief description of the snippet. Documentation Longer description of the snippet and its uses. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}